msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"EE. U. kanpoko bazara, NOWPayments (kosto gutxienak, zuzenean zure "
"dirurgazkira) gomendatzen dizugu. EE. U. baduzu, Stripe Crypto ere aukera "
"bat da. Zure bisitariek aukeratu dezakete hainbat zerbitzu gaitu ditzazun!"

