"onartuko ditu zure Stripe saldobira (ez zuzenean kriptoa)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"EE. Mbaratuetan bazara, Stripe erabil dezakezu kriptoa zuzenean jasotzeko. "
"Kanpoan bazara, hartu NOWPayments edo CoinGate kontuan zuzenean kriptoa "
"ateratzeko."

